@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mjpvxx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.72)) * (wp.cos(tmp + 0.90) * (v2 + 0.02 / v0 + 0.96)))
    v0 = (v2 / wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.02)))
    tmp = 0.08
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.59)) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.68) + wp.exp(tmp + 0.07)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.80)
    data[tid] = v0
